{"id":370557,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":11}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"读者的话","column":"歌唱总路线","genre":"","count":"90","ytitle":"","mtitle":"创造奇迹上北京","ftitle":"","authors":["陈斌"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人生产大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足干劲赶先进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕困难有毅力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄土能够变成金。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民团结一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能叫泰山大翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相学习苦钻研，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造奇迹上北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海医疗器械厂通讯员　陈斌"}]}